<item>
            <title>[DATAREST-213] Make old presentation available for smooth migration to HAL</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-213</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For people using SD Rest a bit longer, the migration towards HAL could take some time. So I think there a many people, which would really appreciate the opportunity of a smooth migration by default enabling both, the old and the new representation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That would help, to be able to get the bugfixes regarding SDF 4.0 and for example the previously filed sorting bug.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>All.</environment>
