                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="96819" author="olivergierke" created="Sat, 28 Dec 2013 06:21:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve just pushed a fix to put this in place. In the &lt;tt&gt;configureRepositoryRestConfiguration(&#8230;)&lt;/tt&gt; callback, call &lt;tt&gt;setDefaultMediaType(&#8230;)&lt;/tt&gt; to set it to &lt;tt&gt;MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON&lt;/tt&gt;. This will cause the legacy &lt;tt&gt;HttpMessageConverter&lt;/tt&gt; be registered &lt;b&gt;before&lt;/b&gt; the HAL one so that you now only get HAL if you explicitly ask for &lt;tt&gt;application/hal+json&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="96824" author="jhiemer" created="Sat, 28 Dec 2013 07:22:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Perfect, works as expected, now I got some time to make a branch for the migration towards HAL.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
